Image Compression using SVD

using LinearAlgebra 
U,S,V = svd(Float64.(Gray.(utdbnw)))
RGB.(U*diagm(S)*V')

Image Compression using SVD

function compressimg(n)
    RGB.(U[:,1:n]*diagm(S[1:n])*V[:,1:n]')
end
